      <div class="nstar-portrait"><img src="Assets/Personas/joe.png" alt="Joe"></div>
      <div class="nlabel">North star for suppliers &middot; Joe</div>
      <div class="nheadline">Easy onboarding</div>
      <div class="nbody">Self-service first. Onboard once per API. Lighter per test. Published criteria. Tiered routes so smaller suppliers stay in scope.</div>
    </a>
    <a class="nstar hometest" href="HomeTest Operating Model - Persona Priya.html" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;">
      <div class="nstar-portrait"><img src="Assets/Personas/priya.png" alt="Priya"></div>
