      <div class="nheadline">Matchmaker, not counterparty</div>
      <div class="nbody">Sets standards, runs onboarding, manages the framework, builds integration, monitors market health. Does not sign local contracts, own billing, deliver care, or operate logistics.</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  

